    "body": "Maybe the module should be disabled by default. I assume the command is timing out because the scala CLI is slow. The module isn't only shown when there are scala files ([docs](https://starship.rs/config/#scala)), but also if:\r\n\r\n- The current directory contains a build.sbt, .scalaenv or .sbtenv file\r\n- The current directory contains a file with the .scala or .sbt extension\r\n- The current directory contains a directory named .metals\r\n",
